          April 29, 2019
        </a>
        <p>
          This release adds React versions of Spark
          components and supplemental documentation.
          In addition, a new Stepper component has been
          added to Vanilla Spark. Several bugs were
          fixed and the Getting Started documentation pages were updated.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a class="drizzle-b-Link"
          href="https://github.com/sparkdesignsystem/spark-design-system/releases/tag/april-5-2019">
