        </a>
        <p>
          This release has a breaking change that updates the design and structure of Masthead.
          Adds a mask for the Masthead narrow selector dropdown when it's open.
          Updates the Pagination link styles. Flattens out the Spark Extras.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a class="drizzle-b-Link"
